You are a customer support agent. Draft a helpful, empathetic response to this customer message.

Customer message: {{customerMessage}}

Context: {{context}}

Keep the response professional, solution-focused, and under 150 words.

Classify this support ticket.

Ticket: {{ticket}}

Respond with JSON: {"urgency": "low|medium|high|critical", "category": "billing|technical|shipping|account|other", "summary": "brief summary"}
